      "seed": 1276083982,
      "version": 624,
      "versionNonce": 244053812,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783437412300,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Logout session deletion logic is broken\n\nIn crud.py, crud_logout() deletes:\ndb.query(UserSession).filter(UserSession.s\nession_token == session_token).delete()\nBut session_token is stored hashed in the\nDB, while the cookie contains the raw\ntoken\nSo logout will usually fail to remove the\nsession record",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "ZoquhjSjPv9QpbRsAgLGW",
      "originalText": "Logout session deletion logic is broken\n\nIn crud.py, crud_logout() deletes:\ndb.query(UserSession).filter(UserSession.session_token == session_token).delete()\nBut session_token is stored hashed in the DB, while the cookie contains the raw token\nSo logout will usually fail to remove the session record",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "j0NFTG1IS_q4tZQXLeHcl",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 732.0364212593067,
      "y": 129.75629266707153,
      "width": 309,
      "height": 402.91234337533024,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
